            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-offset-2 col-md-8">
                <h4>DISCOUNTS & PERKS</h4>
                <h5>ALL YEAR ROUND</h5>
                <p class="small-text">
                  <li><strong>The Vegan Nest</strong> <em>(Worcester, MA)</em> &mdash; 10% off every day<br></li>
                  <li><strong>WooBerry</strong> <em>(Worcester, MA)</em> &mdash; 10% off every day<br></li>
                  <li><strong>Pizza Palace</strong> <em>(Milford, MA)</em> &mdash; 10% off every day<br></li>
                  <li><strong>Green Hair Company</strong> &mdash; 10% off products every day<br></li>
                  <li><strong>NU Cafe</strong> <em>(Worcester, MA)</em> &mdash; 20% off every Tuesday<br></li>
                  <li><strong>Belmont Vegetarian</strong> <em>(Worcester, MA)</em> &mdash; Free upgrade from medium to large on Thursdays<br></li>
